0.1.name: wordpress/aeiou
0.1.description:
AEIOU is a powerfull plugin that export all WordPress users info into an XML file including user settings and options and allow you to import the same data file into a new WordPress keeping all user informations about the users including the Buddypress XProfile data of each user.

Dependencies

AEIOU requires SimpleXML PHP library to import data. Nothing more than wordpress is required for the export.
